{"tid":511083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每天貼4張赤足照　她月賺16.7萬元","createTime":"2017-12-27T06:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T23:10:00.000Z","uid":66943,"like":16,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"3401e736d7705e9987a070cb3b7cc3516c3bc837","tid":511083,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171020/1225677/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171020%2F1225677%2F&d=hfWUNa6%2FVpXfuI8YhkX16p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f0f2d878\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171020%2F1225677%2F&h=a30bea59\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171020/1225677/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171020/640_cbedf9b79ec782bf5795540819245446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171020%2F640_cbedf9b79ec782bf5795540819245446.jpg&h=f2a0a616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻攝自《每日星報》<br />\n加拿大32歲女子古德(Jessica Gould)是位名符其實的「網紅」，她在《Instagram》上有超過萬名追隨者，這些人不只欣賞分享她每天上傳的照片，更會主動匯錢、送禮「打賞」她，古德現在每個月光靠此平均就能賺進4200英鎊(約台幣16.7萬元)！<br />\n<br />\n古德不會在網路上開直播、唱歌跳舞耍寶，她每天做的，就是上傳4張「裸足」的照片，滿足來自各地的「戀足癖」。古德認為自己的工作，就是個「戀物癖女模」。<br />\n<br />\n「我從來沒想過，會有人那麼喜歡我的腳」，「長久以來，我都無法想像我有多離譜，或者說，有一天我會發現，原來自己已經深陷在戀物癖的世界裡無法自拔了」。古德最初只是上傳一些自己赤腳的照片，但一切就從她開始收到一些願意為他的赤腳「奉獻」男人的訊息後起了變化。<br />\n<br />\n「當這類的訊息越來越多，我開始相信許多人會為了這項『榮譽』付錢的，很快地，我就知道要怎樣利用這些照片，來增加更多潛在的客戶」。現在，古德在《IG》上擁有超過一萬名追隨者，每天她要做的，就是上傳最多4張新拍的裸足照片。<br />\n<br />\n古德會在自己每張裸足照片底下，加上「#findom」的主題標籤(Hashtag)，也就是「financial domination」的簡寫，這個字在戀物癖的世界裡，代表對女性的服從(submissive)，也是對女性財務上的奉獻，因為「匯錢給女王能刺激他們的性慾」。古德在自己的介紹中，就備註了網路支付PayPal的帳號，這樣戀足者就可以直接匯錢給她，她還強調：「我們不做傷害性或不安全的事」(Nothing we do is harmful or unsafe)。「我所做的事，是和客戶間權力的交換，我相信我們彼此都在服務對方，沒有什麼好批判的。我扮演著一種角色，他們則乞求我來扮演這個角色，無論動機是天生的性慾，還是其他任何原因」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171020/640_ff145fb771bc725838f0d4b1f8ff49cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171020%2F640_ff145fb771bc725838f0d4b1f8ff49cb.jpg&h=84c470de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/8f/bd/44/8fbd44c5694d984bf27fe00434ccfe9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F8f%2Fbd%2F44%2F8fbd44c5694d984bf27fe00434ccfe9e.jpg&h=ec9020df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac6ef4a980ea192cd3dfeb820b8365263a8f20d6","tid":511083,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30aed14f109782f918f7ab4b4cd2f4753011959","tid":511083,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>@老腦再世_</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a566d73d71061b493d5125e9bd28b5ad2c5dc488","tid":511083,"uid":41116,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"ig 大把正過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd46afd7f0ce0a49f1f0f9cee1a2407d097f56","tid":511083,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afcc9ddf8a7c7343c3edba69dc53ab967ed3b07","tid":511083,"uid":49853,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ig 大把正過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlink?"},{"pid":"777c784855f71138762a5d1bd68499a6cb0849b0","tid":511083,"uid":101390,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"32歲個樣成個50歲阿婆咁 <br />\n鬼婆衰老速度接近音速"},{"pid":"7c503151a55b1a95